OL,3,C'We've Lost Everything': Flood
OL,4,Cdestroys woman's home and business
OL,6,FVideo report by Anna Youssef
OL,8,FA woman says she has lost everything
OL,9,Fafter flood waters ruined her home and
OL,10,Fbusiness.
OL,12,FNikki Campion's home and salon, Nikki
OL,13,F& Co, were destroyed when severe
OL,14,Fflooding hit the Trafford area of
OL,15,FGreater Manchester on New Year's Day.
OL,17,FThe 56-year-old, from Urmston, says
OL,18,Fshe is "devastated" and claims it
OL,19,Fcould have been avoided.
