OL,3,C'We've Lost Everything': Flood
OL,4,Cdestroys woman's home and business
OL,6,F"I've been on to the Environment
OL,7,Fagency for the last five years,
OL,8,Fthey've been out and done nothing,
OL,9,Fbeen out and done nothing, been out
OL,10,Fand done nothing," she says.
OL,12,FSpeaking from her water-damaged
OL,13,Fproperty, Nikki described the
OL,14,Femotional toll of the disaster: "I am
OL,15,Fdevastated, absolutely devastated.
OL,17,F"We have lost everything - beds,
OL,18,Ffurniture, the lot. Everything is
OL,19,Fruined. We'll have to start all over
OL,20,Fagain somehow."
