OL,6,FNikki, who lives with her husband
OL,7,FMatt, 61, said their neighbourhood had
OL,8,Freceived flood alerts before, but
OL,9,Fnothing like this.
OL,11,F"We got a text at 5.40am, we get them
OL,12,Fall the time saying flood alert," she
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,F"Looked out at six o'clock, no water
OL,16,Fat all, by 7.50am you could hear it
OL,17,Funderneath the house but it was still
OL,18,Flower than the steps and by 9.30am our
OL,19,Fhouse was just underwater and it
OL,20,Fcarried on rising till 7.30 that
OL,21,Fnight."
