OL,6,FThe grandmother of three said she
OL,7,Ffeels abandoned by the Environment
OL,8,FAgency, blaming years of inaction on
OL,9,Fproblems she reported with the nearby
OL,10,FOld Eea Brook.
OL,12,F"We've reported issues with the brook
OL,13,Fsince we moved here five years ago.
OL,14,FIt's full of silt and needs cleaning.
OL,15,F(The Environment Agency) came out a
OL,16,Ffew weeks ago but said there wasn't
OL,17,Fmuch they could do because it was such
OL,18,Fa mess. They've done nothing about
OL,19,Fit," she said.
