OL,6,FNikki added that the brook's condition
OL,7,Fwas a disaster waiting to happen and
OL,8,Faccused the agency of failing to
OL,9,Fprevent the flooding.
OL,11,FThe Campions are not alone, other
OL,12,Fhomes in their community have also
OL,13,Fbeen severely affected, with one
OL,14,Fneighbour's house still submerged.
