OL,6,FDespite the devastation, Nikki said
OL,7,Fshe and her husband received
OL,8,Finvaluable help from people in the
OL,9,Flocal community who helped clear the
OL,10,Fwater and begin cleaning up. However,
OL,11,Fthe aftermath remains overwhelming,
OL,12,Fwith a "devastating mess" left behind.
OL,14,F"We've had about 80 people here in the
OL,15,Flast two days, I mean, we've moved
OL,16,Fmountains. Nobody would know we'd had
OL,17,Fa flood.
OL,19,F"We're just going to have to build it
OL,20,Fback, It's material things, my family
OL,21,Fare safe."
