OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for the
OL,7,FEnvironment Agency expressed sympathy
OL,8,Ffor those affected and highlighted
OL,9,Fongoing efforts to manage flood risks
OL,10,Fnationwide.
OL,12,F"Environment Agency teams have been
OL,13,Fworking around the clock over the New
OL,14,FYear, operating flood defences, taking
OL,15,Faction to reduce the impact of
OL,16,Fflooding, issuing flood warnings, and
OL,17,Fsupporting communities, including in
OL,18,FGreater Manchester," the statement
OL,19,Fsaid.
